"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"I wouldn’t say I was a nay-sayer of web3 and crypto. I just felt that there’s still a lot education and unlearning that has to happen for it to get to the masses.\\n\\nI may be underestimating the next generation of internet users though. Kids are smart.\\n\\nAnyway, I am trying to get hang of it. \\n\\nAnd I can experience some of the fundamental things that are different from the old internet.\\n\\nOne example being logging in via a wallet. I have a wallet and that’s all I need to login into most web3 sites. \\n\\nAnother would be payments I assume. I haven’t bought/used any thing in my main wallet yet. But assume that’s also a matter of clicks. \\n\\nAll this is kind of exciting. I can already see things that wouldn’t be possible in the old internet but will be rudimentary in web3.  \\n Things like micro-payments to creators. Or pay-per-article on news sites. \\n\\nI am yet to explore more stuff. Like what’s with NFTs? I am seeking the non-financial side of it. \\n\\nAnd not to forget the DAO and creator coins and stuff. I’ll do that all tonight.\\n\\n\\\\~ Chand + Redbull\",\"timestamp\":1634230677,\"title\":\"Trying to get a hang of it\"},\"digest\":\"6QkXcQ7Q8MQLwJt5auuxCKek0RF1H77KbczKNC0ctC4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xAb7639ACc8924923B51270Db555EE3A429E97D4b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"qm7OXVAsRycyn8rou1hiX-UVWTni9Y7yt0OuC0f-bb8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"l6w3bkNUX0VoC_e3uZmCVNVdWHHQdBCggJCRjKewGoU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"JSo1o_TQuOfMCyHRBNUiFQwnXKXrlaWAi3M4tgzR9TOFQoR-AN0MzNeq0FkiLZfIVWCLCfnqRNj3Iouvmg81-A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa03a8e798a3d36ecde7fce9104effa0243a3d1909dd6d2df2f09d859b872226d08f7fb9f6d333883e58e8785b16fd2371408073314dfa143beebe9b0abea54f61b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],